- gradient transition tutorial by stackoverflow
- answer: https://stackoverflow.com/a/63848864
- lightbox tutorial by shythemes
- title and description are from "tokki" by ciki

note: everything's editable in the 'customize' panel, save for the likes/dislikes in the 'about' panel. you'll have to go into the code for that.


